{"type":"message","id":"083d0dbe","parentId":"fb3d1fe9","timestamp":"2026-04-14T11:31:48.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me answer the user's question about whether this is based on latest market data and whether recommended buy prices should be stated.\n\nLooking at the JSON data, I can see:\n\n1. The report was generated at `2026-04-13 19:38:57` for trade date `2026-04-13`\n2. Each candidate has:\n   - `ai_realtime_price`: \"15.22\" (for example, 远东股份)\n   - `ai_realtime_change_pct`: \"-2.44\" \n   - `ai_realtime_source`: \"tushare\"\n   - `ai_realtime_confirmed`: \"True\"\n   - `ai_analysis_time`: \"2026-04-13T17:59:40.318292\"\n   - `ai_no_position_advice`: Contains the recommended buy price info like \"可在15.22元附近或回踩至15.40元（MA5）时，分批建立底仓\"\n\nSo the realtime price IS included (`ai_realtime_price`), and the `ai_no_position_advice` field effectively tells you the recommended buy price (or price range near MA5).\n\n\nThe preview only shows stock code, name, and score, but the full JSON has all the realtime price data and specific buy advice—the preview is missing this detail. I need to clarify what the preview displays versus what's actually available in the complete report.","thinkingSignature":"5f16500ad3c6e42eebac565f9b52a697dea7e9dfe6724891fdb24fef9dfe37f1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n没有完成。找到了报告，给你解释一下：\n\n**关于张玲的问题，回答如下：**\n\n**1. 是不是按最新行情计算？**\n是的。报告里每个候选都有：\n- `ai_realtime_price` — 实时价格（如远东股份 15.22元）\n- `ai_realtime_change_pct` — 当日涨跌幅\n- `ai_analysis_time` — 最后更新时间\n\n**2. 推荐买入价是否写明？**\n有，但藏在详细字段里。每条候选的 `ai_no_position_advice` 字段就是买入建议，例如：\n\n> 远东股份：空仓者建议：可在**15.22元**附近或回踩至**15.40元**（MA5）时，分批建立底仓。\n\n但预览里只显示了股票代码+评分，**没有把推荐买入价/建议买卖点单独列出来**。这就是你说的改进点。\n\n---\n\n**现在回答 openclaw-control-ui 的问题：**\n\n之前张玲的任务还在待处理状态——我在查文件时花了些时间。现在已经拿到完整的 `today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json`，可以确认：\n\n- 报告数据基于 2026-04-13 收盘数据（昨日收盘后 19:38 生成）\n- 三个 TOP3 候选（浙文互联/天龙集团/飞龙股份）的实时价格和买入建议都在 JSON 里\n- 报告本身是